name_pretty: Google Cloud Bigquery Datapolicies V1beta1 API
ruby-cloud-description: google-cloud-bigquery-datapolicies-v1beta1 is the official client library for the Google Cloud Bigquery Datapolicies V1beta1 API. Note that google-cloud-bigquery-datapolicies-v1beta1 is a version-specific client library. For most uses, we recommend installing the main client library google-cloud-bigquery-datapolicies instead. See the readme for more details.
